subtitleNullable: I am sharing my personal mood tracking data with Kaggle Community.
descriptionNullable:
### Context

I was struggling with mental illness since the start of 2017 and this app has made me better by noting down my mod on daily basis and what type of activities affects the most, In my case, Dota  2 was an anomaly other than that there have been many cases when I looked back at yearly stats and wonder about on how can I get better analysis from my Data so here I am presenting you my personal data and wanting you to come up with an explanation about what activities effects most and blow my mind. 

### Content

**Daylio** is Self-Care Bullet Journal with Goals
Mood Diary & Happiness Tracker. The Data contains, Date -> from 03/02/2018 to 16/04/2021, full data, time, Weekdays, moods, and activities that effect the mood.


### Acknowledgements

I want to thank my sister and other people who have to help me during the worst time of my life when I was struggling with depression and this app who have kept me grounded.
